---
import Icon from "astro-icon";
import FlipCard from "./FlipCard.astro";
import Section from "./Section.astro";
---

<Section addons="flex flex-col items-center justify-around relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="hero-background"></div>
  <div class="flex flex-col items-center py-24 relative z-10">
    <h1
      class="font-[1100] text-5xl/[1.1] lg:text-6xl/[1.1] relative"
    >
      Creando el futuro con Agentes de IA
    </h1>
    <p
      class="text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-3xl text-center mt-6 mb-12 font-light"
    >
      Soy Johan, especialista en desarrollo de agentes de inteligencia artificial.
      Me dedico a crear sistemas autónomos inteligentes que potencian las capacidades
      humanas y resuelven problemas complejos de forma eficiente.
    </p>
    <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-3xl text-center mt-2 font-light">
      ¿Cómo puedo ayudarte con agentes de IA?
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center mt-6 gap-4">
      <div
        class="bg-gradient-to-r from-secondary to-[#ff5c2e] hover:scale-110 transition-all rounded-full"
      >
        <a
          href="/cv-johan-lozano.pdf"
          target="_blank"
          class="flex justify-center items-center gap-3 py-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-black/[0.45] via-black/30 to-black/[0.45] px-3 m-[3px] w-56 rounded-full"
        >
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            class="h-6 w-6 text-white animate-fade"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="currentColor"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="0.5"
          >
            <path
              d="M18.944 11.112C18.507 7.67 15.56 5 12 5 9.244 5 6.85 6.611 5.757 9.15 3.609 9.792 2 11.82 2 14c0 2.757 2.243 5 5 5h11c2.206 0 4-1.794 4-4a4.01 4.01 0 0 0-3.056-3.888zM13 14v3h-2v-3H8l4-5 4 5h-3z"
            ></path>
          </svg>
          <span class="text-sm sm:text-base">Descargar CV</span>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div
        class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[#ff5c2e] to-primary hover:scale-110 transition-all rounded-full"
      >
        <a
          href="https://wa.me/573142968931"
          target="_blank"
          class="flex justify-center items-center gap-3 px-3 py-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-black/[0.45] via-black/30 to-black/[0.45] m-[3px] w-56 rounded-full"
        >
          <Icon
            name="ph:whatsapp-logo-duotone"
            class="h-6 w-6 text-white"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="0.5"
          />
          <span class="text-sm sm:text-base">Contactar</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="section-fade"></div>
</Section>
<style>
  .hero-background {
    position: absolute;
    width: 200%;
    height: 200%;
    top: -50%;
    left: -50%;
    background: 
      radial-gradient(circle at 30% 30%, rgba(109, 40, 217, 0.25) 0%, transparent 40%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 70% 60%, rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.2) 0%, transparent 40%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 40% 80%, rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.15) 0%, transparent 30%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 80% 20%, rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.2) 0%, transparent 40%);
    transform: rotate(-10deg);
    z-index: 0;
    animation: pulse 15s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
  }

  .hero-mesh {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width='100' height='100' viewBox='0 0 100 100' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cpath d='M0 0h100v100H0z' fill='none'/%3E%3Cpath d='M0 0v100h100V0H0zm1 1h98v98H1V1z' fill='rgba(255,255,255,0.05)'/%3E%3Cpath d='M1 1h98v98H1V1z' fill='none' stroke='rgba(255,255,255,0.03)' stroke-width='0.25'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
    background-size: 50px 50px;
    backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
    opacity: 0.5;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .section-fade {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -2px;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 150px;
    background: linear-gradient(to top, #030712 10%, transparent 100%);
    z-index: 2;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  @keyframes pulse {
    0% {
      opacity: 0.7;
      transform: rotate(-10deg) scale(1);
    }
    50% {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: rotate(-10deg) scale(1.05);
    }
    100% {
      opacity: 0.8;
      transform: rotate(-10deg) scale(1);
    }
  }
</style>
